        "text": {
          "format": 1,
          "content": "<p><b>What it represents:</b> Food, order, morale, trust in leadership.</p><p><b>Advance when:</b> bandit attacks go unanswered, shortages worsen, public humiliations turn ugly, a scandal leaks.</p><p><b>Reduce when:</b> PCs solve a local crisis, secure trade, expose a threat cleanly, or deliver supplies.</p><p><b>When full:</b> curfew, rationing, mass arrests, and vigilantism. Spellcasting punishments become harsher.</p>"
        },
        "video": { "controls": true, "volume": 0.5 },
